Detailed Description

MbiProvider is the provider to retrieve the MBI record identifier as defined in 3GPP TS 51.011 V4.13.0 and 3GPP TS 31.102 V6.8.0. The record identifier which is returned can be directly be used as the index into the c_mbdn_provider_id phonebook to retrieve its phonenumber and alphaidentifier. An instance of this class is part of the Apoxi Data Control. A pointer to this provider can be retrieved from the main provider via the id:

c_mbi_provider_id

Following column ids are defined: c_mdni_voicemail_id :NumberType: c_mdni_fax_id :NumberType: c_mdni_electronic_mail_id :NumberType: c_mdni_other_id :NumberType: c_mdni_videomail_id :NumberType:

NOTE: Please do not instantiate this class.
